column5: Those are some beasts!
Amazing stuff
Lord Tundra and Geezus!  nice fish!  Where was this?
St Lawrence river....  Fished 12-6am last night and got 15.... Biggest were 6&7 pound double header...
If this is any indicator of how fall fishing will be this year I'm pretty pumped...
Nice!
Wow!  Beauty pics, congrats!
Geeeezus nice!!
Nice eyes that you catch. Your work out at night give good result.  :clapping:
^this guys posts are hilarious,   I hope this is an Omen! The eyes will be moving in on GB soon enough!
Wow those are some monsters, way to go
nice fish
Tankers! Did you get a weight on the biggest? was it that technique you gave me last fall?
wow, incredible night out!
Biggest 2 were both exactly 8.15... So the boys got the same new PBs... Lol... Now they can't trash talk each other....   And yup....
Nice bonus SM as well.
Wow!!  By the looks of things you'll be doing well for the next couple months.  I can't believe the avg size of them, amazing.  Clean looking fish too.

sweet fish man
